        "subject": "LU-2704 llite: GPF in __d_lookup called from ll_statahead_on",
        "message": "LU-2704 llite: GPF in __d_lookup called from ll_statahead_on\n\ndentry_hashtable[] corruption suspected to occur due to a race\nallowed with the lack of dcache_lock protection/lock before\ncalling d_lustre_invalidate() who will itself call directly\n__d_drop(). Adding an Assert to early trigger in such case.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bruno Faccini <bruno.faccini@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I5a1da9b95d8bcc89c9dd38071e828cc9e40b89de\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
